BREAKING: DOH reports 740 new COVID-19 cases (452 Fresh, 288 Late), 10 new deaths, and 159 new recoveries. 

This brings the totals to 23,732 confirmed cases, 1,027 deaths, and 4,895 recoveries as of today, June 10. #COVID19PH | @shailagarde https://t.co/mvsm6TIiM2
